    <p><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l7' data-llen='156:182'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0086', 'WYG', '015-1a' );" name="015-1a" class="pb">[015-1a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l8' data-llen='182:190'>欽定四庫全書</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l9' data-llen='190:211'>　禮書綱目卷十三　　　　　　婺源江永撰</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l10' data-llen='211:224'>士相見禮　　　　賓禮一</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l11' data-llen='224:269'>　經<span class='krp-note'>鄭目録云士以職位相親始承摯相見之禮雜記/㑹葬禮曰相見也反哭而退朋友虞祔而退士相</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l12' data-llen='269:282'>　<span class='krp-note'>見於五禮/屬賓禮</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l13' data-llen='282:305'>士相見之禮贄冬用雉夏用腒左頭奉之曰某也願見</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l14' data-llen='305:342'>無由達某子以命命某見<span class='krp-note'>贄所執以至者君子見於所/尊敬必執贄以將其厚意也</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l15' data-llen='342:389'><span class='krp-note'>士贄用雉者取其耿介交有時别有倫也雉必用死者/為其不可生服也夏用腒備腐臭也左頭頭陽也無由</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l16' data-llen='389:415'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0086', 'WYG', '015-1b' );" name="015-1b" class="pb">[015-1b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l17' data-llen='415:458'><span class='krp-note'>達言久無因縁以自達也某子今所因縁之/姓名也以命者稱述主人之意今文頭為脰</span>主人對曰</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l18' data-llen='458:485'>某子命某見吾子有辱請吾子之就家也某將走見<span class='krp-note'>有/又</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l19' data-llen='485:524'><span class='krp-note'>也某子命某往見今吾子又自辱/來序其意也走猶往也今文無走</span>賓對曰某不足以辱</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l20' data-llen='524:554'>命請終賜見<span class='krp-note'>命謂請吾/子之就家</span>主人對曰某不敢為儀固請吾</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l21' data-llen='554:592'>子之就家也某將走見<span class='krp-note'>不敢為儀言不敢外貌為威儀/忠誠欲往也固如故也今文不</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l22' data-llen='592:630'><span class='krp-note'>為非古文云/固以請也</span>賓對曰某不敢為儀固以請<span class='krp-note'>言如故請終/賜見也今文</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l23' data-llen='630:657'><span class='krp-note'>不為/非</span>主人對曰某也固辭不得命將走見聞吾子稱贄</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l24' data-llen='657:699'>敢辭贄<span class='krp-note'>不得命者不得見許之命也走猶出也稱舉/也辭其贄為其大崇也古文曰某將走見</span>賓</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l25' data-llen='699:725'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0086', 'WYG', '015-2a' );" name="015-2a" class="pb">[015-2a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l26' data-llen='725:757'>對曰某不以贄不敢見<span class='krp-note'>見於所尊敬而/無贄嫌大簡</span>主人對曰某不足</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l27' data-llen='757:790'>以習禮敢固辭<span class='krp-note'>言不足習禮者不敢/當其崇禮來見已</span>賓對曰某也不依</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l28' data-llen='790:822'>於贄不敢見固以請<span class='krp-note'>言依於贄謙自/卑也今文無也</span>主人對曰某也固</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l29' data-llen='822:845'>辭不得命敢不敬從出迎于門外再拜賓答再拜主人</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l30' data-llen='845:868'>揖入門右賓奉贄入門左主人再拜受賓再拜送贄出</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l31' data-llen='868:910'><span class='krp-note'>右就右也左就左也受贄於庭既拜受送/則出矣不受贄於堂下人君也今文無也</span>主人請見賓</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l32' data-llen='910:946'>反見退主人送于門外再拜<span class='krp-note'>請見者為賓崇禮來相接/以矜莊歡心未交也賓反</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l33' data-llen='946:987'><span class='krp-note'>見則燕矣下云凡燕見於君至凡侍坐于君子/博記反見之燕義臣初見於君再拜奠贄而出</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l34' data-llen='987:1013'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0086', 'WYG', '015-2b' );" name="015-2b" class="pb">[015-2b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l35' data-llen='1013:1044'>　　右請見<span class='krp-note'>凡賓主相見之/儀附載於下</span>　記聞始見君子者辭曰</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l36' data-llen='1044:1080'>　　某固願聞名於將命者<span class='krp-note'>君子卿大夫若有異德者/固如故也將猶奉也即君</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l37' data-llen='1080:1123'>　　<span class='krp-note'>子之門而云願以名聞於奉命者謙/逺之也重則云固奉命傳辭出入</span>不得階主<span class='krp-note'>階/上</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l38' data-llen='1123:1164'>　　<span class='krp-note'>進者言賓之辭/不得指斥主人</span>敵者曰某固願見<span class='krp-note'>敵當也願見願/見於將命者謙</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l39' data-llen='1164:1203'>　　<span class='krp-note'>也/</span>罕見曰聞名<span class='krp-note'>罕希也希相見雖於敵者/猶為尊主之辭如於君子</span>亟見曰</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l40' data-llen='1203:1245'>　　朝夕<span class='krp-note'>亟數也於君子則曰某願朝夕聞名於將/命者於敵者則曰某願朝夕見於將命者</span>瞽</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l41' data-llen='1245:1279'>　　曰聞名<span class='krp-note'>瞽無目也以無目/辭不稱見  少儀</span>　同國始相見主人拜</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l42' data-llen='1279:1315'>　　其辱<span class='krp-note'>自外來而拜拜見也自内/來而拜拜辱也  曲禮</span>　凡非弔喪非見</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l43' data-llen='1315:1341'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0086', 'WYG', '015-3a' );" name="015-3a" class="pb">[015-3a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l44' data-llen='1341:1379'>　　國君無不答拜者<span class='krp-note'>禮尚往來喪賓不答拜不自賓/客也國君見士不答其拜士賤</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l45' data-llen='1379:1414'>　　<span class='krp-note'>上同/</span>　凡與客入者每門讓於客<span class='krp-note'>下賓也敵者迎/于大門外聘禮</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l46' data-llen='1414:1450'>　　<span class='krp-note'>曰君近賓/於大門内</span>客至於寢門則主人請入為席<span class='krp-note'>為猶敷/也雖君</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l47' data-llen='1450:1487'>　　<span class='krp-note'>亦/然</span>然後出迎客客固辭<span class='krp-note'>又譲/先入</span>主人肅客而入<span class='krp-note'>肅進/也進</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l48' data-llen='1487:1522'>　　<span class='krp-note'>客謂/道之</span>主人入門而右客入門而左<span class='krp-note'>右就其右/左就其左</span>主人</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l49' data-llen='1522:1550'>　　就東階客就西階客若降等則就主人之階<span class='krp-note'>降下/也謂</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l50' data-llen='1550:1587'>　　<span class='krp-note'>大夫於君士於大夫也不敢輙/由其階卑統於尊不敢自專</span>主人固辭然後客</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l51' data-llen='1587:1614'>　　復就西階<span class='krp-note'>復其/正</span>主人與客讓登主人先登客從之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l52' data-llen='1614:1640'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0086', 'WYG', '015-3b' );" name="015-3b" class="pb">[015-3b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l53' data-llen='1640:1679'>　　拾級聚足<span class='krp-note'>拾當為涉聲之誤也級等也涉等/聚足謂前足躡一等後足從之併</span>連步</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l54' data-llen='1679:1712'>　　以上<span class='krp-note'>重蹉跌也連步謂/足相隨不相過也</span>上於東階則先右足上於</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l55' data-llen='1712:1743'>　　西階則先左足<span class='krp-note'>近於相鄉/敬  同上</span>　席南鄉北鄉以西方</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l56' data-llen='1743:1777'>　　為上東鄉西鄉以南方為上<span class='krp-note'>布席無常此其順之/也上謂席端也坐在</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l57' data-llen='1777:1812'>　　<span class='krp-note'>陽則上左坐/在隂則上右</span>若非飲食之客則布席席間函丈<span class='krp-note'>謂/講</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l58' data-llen='1812:1854'>　　<span class='krp-note'>問之客也函猶容也講問宜相對容丈足以/指畫也飲食之客布席於牖前丈或為杖</span>主人</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l59' data-llen='1854:1893'>　　跪正席<span class='krp-note'>雖來講問猶以客/禮待之異於弟子</span>客跪撫席而辭<span class='krp-note'>撫之者/答主人</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l60' data-llen='1893:1930'>　　<span class='krp-note'>之親/正席</span>客徹重席主人固辭<span class='krp-note'>徹去也去重席/謙也再辭曰固</span>客踐席</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l61' data-llen='1930:1956'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0086', 'WYG', '015-4a' );" name="015-4a" class="pb">[015-4a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l62' data-llen='1956:1994'>　　乃坐<span class='krp-note'>客安主人乃敢/安也講問宜坐</span>主人不問客不先舉<span class='krp-note'>客自外/來宜問</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l63' data-llen='1994:2027'>　　<span class='krp-note'>其安否無恙及所/為來故  同上</span>　始入而辭曰辭矣即席曰可</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l64' data-llen='2027:2068'>　　矣<span class='krp-note'>可猶止也謂擯者為賓主之節也始入/則告之辭至就席則止其辭  少儀</span>　氾埽</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l65' data-llen='2068:2097'>　　曰埽埽席前曰拚拚席不以鬛執箕膺擖<span class='krp-note'>鬛謂帚/也帚恒</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l66' data-llen='2097:2136'>　　<span class='krp-note'>埽地不㓗清也膺親也擖舌也持/箕将去糞者以舌自鄉  同上</span>　其未有燭而</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l67' data-llen='2136:2169'>　　後至者則以在者告道瞽亦然<span class='krp-note'>為其不見意欲知/之也師冕見及階</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l68' data-llen='2169:2208'>　　<span class='krp-note'>子曰階也及席子曰席也皆坐子/告之曰某在斯某在斯  同上</span>　請見不請退</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l69' data-llen='2208:2225'>　　<span class='krp-note'>去止不敢自/由  同上</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l70' data-llen='2225:2251'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0086', 'WYG', '015-4b' );" name="015-4b" class="pb">[015-4b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l71' data-llen='2251:2274'>主人復見之以其贄曰曏者吾子辱使某見請還贄於</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l72' data-llen='2274:2317'>將命者<span class='krp-note'>復見之者禮尚往來也以其贄謂曏時所執/來者也曏曩也將猶傳也傳命者謂擯相者</span>主</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l73' data-llen='2317:2346'>人對曰某也既得見矣敢辭<span class='krp-note'>讓其來/答已也</span>賓對曰某也非敢</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l74' data-llen='2346:2380'>求見請還贄於將命者<span class='krp-note'>言不敢求見嫌褻主人/不敢當也今文無也</span>主人對</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l75' data-llen='2380:2408'>曰某也既得見矣敢固辭<span class='krp-note'>固如/故也</span>賓對曰某不敢以聞固</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l76' data-llen='2408:2439'>以請於將命者<span class='krp-note'>言不敢以聞/又益不敢當</span>主人對曰某也固辭不得</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l77' data-llen='2439:2471'>命敢不從<span class='krp-note'>許受之也異日則/出迎同日則否</span>賓奉贄入主人再拜受賓</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l78' data-llen='2471:2486'>再拜送贄出主人送于門外再拜</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l79' data-llen='2486:2512'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0086', 'WYG', '015-5a' );" name="015-5a" class="pb">[015-5a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l80' data-llen='2512:2519'>　　右復見</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l81' data-llen='2519:2542'>士見於大夫終辭其贄於其入也一拜其辱也賓退送</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l82' data-llen='2542:2587'>再拜<span class='krp-note'>終辭其贄以將不親答也凡不答而受其贄唯君/於臣耳大夫於士不出迎入一拜正禮也送再拜</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l83' data-llen='2587:2594'><span class='krp-note'>尊/賓</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l84' data-llen='2594:2617'>　　右士見大夫　記大夫士相見雖貴賤不敵主人</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l85' data-llen='2617:2644'>　　敬客則先拜客客敬主人則先拜主人<span class='krp-note'>尊/賢</span>士見於</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l86' data-llen='2644:2671'>　　大夫大夫拜其辱<span class='krp-note'>曲/禮</span>　士於尊者先拜進面答之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l87' data-llen='2671:2701'>　　拜則走<span class='krp-note'>士往見卿大夫卿大夫出/迎答拜亦辟也  玊藻</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l88' data-llen='2701:2727'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0086', 'WYG', '015-5b' );" name="015-5b" class="pb">[015-5b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l89' data-llen='2727:2750'>若嘗為臣者則禮辭其贄曰某也辭不得命不敢固辭</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l90' data-llen='2750:2787'><span class='krp-note'>禮辭一辭其贄而許也將不/答而聴其以贄入有臣道也</span>賓入奠贄再拜主人答壹</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l91' data-llen='2787:2820'>拜<span class='krp-note'>奠贄尊卑異不親/授也古文壹為一</span>賓出使擯者還其贄于門外曰某</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l92' data-llen='2820:2854'>也使某還贄<span class='krp-note'>還其贄者/辟正君也</span>賓對曰某也既得見矣敢辭<span class='krp-note'>辭/君</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l93' data-llen='2854:2884'><span class='krp-note'>還其贄也/今文無也</span>擯者對曰某也命某某非敢為儀也敢以請</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l94' data-llen='2884:2913'><span class='krp-note'>還贄者請/使受之</span>賓對曰某也夫子之賤私不足以踐禮敢固</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l95' data-llen='2913:2952'>辭<span class='krp-note'>家臣稱私踐行也言某臣也不足以/行賓客禮賓客所不答者不受贄</span>擯者對曰某也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l96' data-llen='2952:2984'>使某不敢為儀也固以請<span class='krp-note'>言使某尊君也或/言命某傳言耳</span>賓對曰某</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l97' data-llen='2984:3010'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0086', 'WYG', '015-6a' );" name="015-6a" class="pb">[015-6a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l98' data-llen='3010:3032'>固辭不得命敢不從再拜受<span class='krp-note'>受其贄/而去之</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l99' data-llen='3032:3055'>　　右嘗為臣者見　記大夫於其臣雖賤必答拜之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l100' data-llen='3055:3069'>　　<span class='krp-note'>辟正君/  曲禮</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l101' data-llen='3069:3098'>下大夫相見以鴈飾之以布維之以索如執雉<span class='krp-note'>鴈取知/時飛翔</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l102' data-llen='3098:3134'><span class='krp-note'>有行列也飾之以布謂裁縫/衣其身也維謂繫聮其足</span>上大夫相見以羔飾之以</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l103' data-llen='3134:3168'>布四維之結于面左頭如麛執之<span class='krp-note'>上大夫卿也羔取其/從帥羣而不黨也面</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l104' data-llen='3168:3215'><span class='krp-note'>前也繫聮四足交出背上於胸前結之也如麛執之者/秋獻麛有成如之或曰麛孤之摯也其禮盖謂左執前</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l105' data-llen='3215:3249'><span class='krp-note'>足右執後足/今文頭為脰</span>如士相見之禮<span class='krp-note'>大夫雖贄異/其儀猶如士</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l106' data-llen='3249:3275'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0086', 'WYG', '015-6b' );" name="015-6b" class="pb">[015-6b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l107' data-llen='3275:3315'>　　右大夫相見<span class='krp-note'>本文此下有始見於君若他邦之人/及燕見於君三條今並入曲禮臣禮</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l108' data-llen='3315:3323'>　　<span class='krp-note'>篇/</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l109' data-llen='3323:3360'>凡言非對也妥而後傳言<span class='krp-note'>凡言謂已為君言事也妥安/坐也傳言猶出言也若君問</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l110' data-llen='3360:3393'><span class='krp-note'>可對則對不待安/坐也古文妥為綏</span>與君言言使臣與大人言言事君與</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l111' data-llen='3393:3416'>老者言言使弟子與幼者言言孝弟于父兄與衆言言</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l112' data-llen='3416:3451'>忠信慈祥與居官者言言忠信<span class='krp-note'>博陳燕見言語之儀也/言使臣者使臣之禮也</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l113' data-llen='3451:3481'><span class='krp-note'>大人卿大夫也言事君者臣事君/以忠也祥善也居官謂士以下</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l114' data-llen='3481:3487'>　　右言</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l115' data-llen='3487:3513'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0086', 'WYG', '015-7a' );" name="015-7a" class="pb">[015-7a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l116' data-llen='3513:3540'>凡與大夫言始視面中視抱卒視面毋改衆皆若是<span class='krp-note'>始/視</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l117' data-llen='3540:3587'><span class='krp-note'>面謂觀其顔色可傳言未也中視抱容其思之且為敬/也卒視面察其納己言否也毋改謂傳言見答應之間</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l118' data-llen='3587:3634'><span class='krp-note'>當正容體以待之毋自變動為嫌解惰不虚心也衆謂/諸卿大夫同在此者皆若是其視之儀無異也古文毋</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l119' data-llen='3634:3670'><span class='krp-note'>作無今文/衆為終</span>若父則遊目毋上於面毋下於帶<span class='krp-note'>子於父主/孝不主敬</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l120' data-llen='3670:3706'><span class='krp-note'>所視廣也因觀安否何如也/今文父為甫古文毋為無</span>若不言立則視足坐則視</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l121' data-llen='3706:3721'>膝<span class='krp-note'>不言則伺其/行起而已</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l122' data-llen='3721:3756'>　　右視<span class='krp-note'>凡賓主飲食之禮本經/不具今以他記附于下</span>　記凡進食之禮左</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l123' data-llen='3756:3788'>　　殽右胾食居人之左羮居人之右<span class='krp-note'>皆便食也殽骨/體也胾切肉也</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l124' data-llen='3788:3814'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0086', 'WYG', '015-7b' );" name="015-7b" class="pb">[015-7b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l125' data-llen='3814:3854'>　　<span class='krp-note'>食飯屬也居人左右明/其近也殽在俎胾在豆</span>膾炙處外醯醬處内<span class='krp-note'>殽胾/之外</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l126' data-llen='3854:3898'>　　<span class='krp-note'>内也近醯醤者食/之主膾炙皆在豆</span>蔥㳿處末<span class='krp-note'>㳿烝蔥也處醯醬之/左言末者殊加也㳿</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l127' data-llen='3898:3942'>　　<span class='krp-note'>在/豆</span>酒漿處右<span class='krp-note'>處羮之右此言若酒若漿耳兩有之/則左酒右漿此大夫士與賓客燕食</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l128' data-llen='3942:3981'>　　<span class='krp-note'>之禮其禮食則宜/放公食大夫禮云</span>以脯脩置者左朐右末<span class='krp-note'>亦便食/也屈中</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l129' data-llen='3981:4021'>　　<span class='krp-note'>曰朐/曲禮</span>　　羞濡魚者進尾<span class='krp-note'>擗之由後鯁肉易離也/乾魚進首擗之由前理</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l130' data-llen='4021:4065'>　　<span class='krp-note'>易析/也</span>冬右腴<span class='krp-note'>陽氣在下/腴腹下也</span>夏右鰭<span class='krp-note'>陽氣在上/鰭脊也</span>祭膴<span class='krp-note'>膴/大</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l131' data-llen='4065:4104'>　　<span class='krp-note'>臠謂刳魚腹讀/如冔  少儀</span>　客若降等執食興辭<span class='krp-note'>辭者辭主/人之臨已</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l132' data-llen='4104:4138'>　　<span class='krp-note'>食若欲食/於堂下然</span>主人興辭於客然後客坐<span class='krp-note'>復/坐</span>主人延客</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l133' data-llen='4138:4164'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0086', 'WYG', '015-8a' );" name="015-8a" class="pb">[015-8a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l134' data-llen='4164:4205'>　　祭<span class='krp-note'>延道也祭祭先也君子有事/不忘本也客不降等則先祭</span>祭食祭所先進<span class='krp-note'>主/人</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l135' data-llen='4205:4246'>　　<span class='krp-note'>所先進先祭之所後/進後祭之如其次</span>殽之序徧祭之<span class='krp-note'>謂胾炙㑹也/以其本出于</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l136' data-llen='4246:4281'>　　<span class='krp-note'>牲體也公食禮魚腊/湇醤不祭也  曲禮</span>　凡羞有俎者則於俎内祭</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l137' data-llen='4281:4315'>　　<span class='krp-note'>俎於人為横不得/祭於間也  少儀</span>　唯水漿不祭若祭為已偞卑</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l138' data-llen='4315:4355'>　　<span class='krp-note'>水漿非盛饌也已猶大也祭之為大/有所畏廹臣於君則祭之  玉藻</span>　三飯主人</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l139' data-llen='4355:4391'>　　延客食胾然後辯殽<span class='krp-note'>先食胾後食殽殽尊也凡/食殽辯於肩食肩則飽也</span>主</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l140' data-llen='4391:4429'>　　人未辯客不虚口<span class='krp-note'>俟主人也虚口謂酳也客自敵/以上其酳不待主人飽主人不</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l141' data-llen='4429:4463'>　　<span class='krp-note'>先飽/也</span>侍食於長者主人親饋則拜而食<span class='krp-note'>勸長者食/耳雖賤不</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l142' data-llen='4463:4489'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0086', 'WYG', '015-8b' );" name="015-8b" class="pb">[015-8b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l143' data-llen='4489:4526'>　　<span class='krp-note'>得執食興辭拜/而己示敬也</span>主人不親饋則不拜而食<span class='krp-note'>以其禮/於已不</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l144' data-llen='4526:4567'>　　<span class='krp-note'>隆/</span>共食不飽<span class='krp-note'>謙也謂共羮/飯之大器也</span>共飯不澤手<span class='krp-note'>謂汗生不/㓗也澤謂</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l145' data-llen='4567:4611'>　　<span class='krp-note'>捼莎也禮飯以/手澤或為擇</span>毋摶飯<span class='krp-note'>為欲致/飽不謙</span>毋放飯<span class='krp-note'>去手餘飯/於器中人</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l146' data-llen='4611:4653'>　　<span class='krp-note'>所/穢</span>毋流歠<span class='krp-note'>大歠嫌/欲疾</span>毋咤食<span class='krp-note'>嫌薄/之</span>毋齧骨<span class='krp-note'>為有聲/響不敬</span>毋</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l147' data-llen='4653:4688'>　　反魚肉<span class='krp-note'>為已厯口/人所穢</span>毋投與狗骨<span class='krp-note'>為其賤飲/食之物</span>毋固獲</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l148' data-llen='4688:4725'>　　<span class='krp-note'>為其不亷也欲專/之曰固爭取曰獲</span>毋揚飯飯黍毋以箸毋嚃羮<span class='krp-note'>亦/嫌</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l149' data-llen='4725:4770'>　　<span class='krp-note'>欲疾也嚃/為不嚼菜</span>毋絮羮<span class='krp-note'>為其詳於味/也絮猶調也</span>毋刺齒<span class='krp-note'>為其㺯口/也口容止</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l150' data-llen='4770:4802'>　　毋歠醢<span class='krp-note'>亦嫌詳於味也/歠者為其淡故</span>客絮羮主人辭不能亨客</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l151' data-llen='4802:4828'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0086', 'WYG', '015-9a' );" name="015-9a" class="pb">[015-9a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l152' data-llen='4828:4860'>　　歠醢主人辭以窶<span class='krp-note'>優/賓</span>濡肉齒決<span class='krp-note'>決猶/㫁也</span>乾肉不齒決</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l153' data-llen='4860:4901'>　　<span class='krp-note'>堅宜/用手</span>毋嘬炙<span class='krp-note'>為其貪食甚也嘬謂一舉盡/臠特牲少牢嚌之加于俎</span>卒食客</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l154' data-llen='4901:4936'>　　自前跪徹飯齊以授相者<span class='krp-note'>謙也自從也齊醤屬也/相者主人賛饌者公食</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l155' data-llen='4936:4973'>　　<span class='krp-note'>大夫禮賓卒食北面/取粱與醤以降也</span>主人興辭於客然後客坐<span class='krp-note'>不/聴</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l156' data-llen='4973:5005'>　　<span class='krp-note'>親徹/曲禮</span>　　侍食於先生異爵者後祭先飯<span class='krp-note'>謙/也</span>客祭</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l157' data-llen='5005:5035'>　　主人辭曰不足祭也<span class='krp-note'>祭者盛主/人之饌也</span>客飱主人辭以疏</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l158' data-llen='5035:5071'>　　<span class='krp-note'>飱者美主人之食/也疏之言麤也</span>主人自置其醬則客自徹之<span class='krp-note'>敬/主</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l159' data-llen='5071:5111'>　　<span class='krp-note'>人也徹奠於/序端  玉藻</span>　客自徹辭焉則止<span class='krp-note'>主人辭其/徹  少儀</span>　凡</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l160' data-llen='5111:5137'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0086', 'WYG', '015-9b' );" name="015-9b" class="pb">[015-9b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l161' data-llen='5137:5165'>　　侑食不盡食食於人不飽<span class='krp-note'>謙也/玉藻</span>　　孔子食於季</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l162' data-llen='5165:5198'>　　氏不辭不食肉而飱<span class='krp-note'>以其待已及饌/非禮也  同上</span>　孔子曰吾</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l163' data-llen='5198:5229'>　　食於少施氏而飽少施氏食我以禮<span class='krp-note'>言貴其以禮/待己而為之</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l164' data-llen='5229:5267'>　　<span class='krp-note'>飽也時人倨慢若季氏則不以禮/矣少施氏魯惠公子施父之後</span>吾祭作而辭曰</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l165' data-llen='5267:5290'>　　疏食不足祭也吾飱作而辭曰疏食也不敢以傷</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l166' data-llen='5290:5334'>　　吾子<span class='krp-note'>雜記食案家語孔子食於季氏食祭主人不/辭不  亦不飲而飱子夏問曰禮也孔子曰</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l167' data-llen='5334:5379'>　　<span class='krp-note'>非禮也從主人也吾食於少施氏而飽云云主人/不以禮客不敢盡禮主人盡禮則客不敢不盡禮</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l168' data-llen='5379:5415'>　　<span class='krp-note'>也/</span>　有盛饌必變色而作<span class='krp-note'>敬主人之禮非以/其饌也  鄉黨</span>　凡</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l169' data-llen='5415:5442'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0086', 'WYG', '015-10a' );" name="015-10a" class="pb">[015-10a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l170' data-llen='5442:5465'>　　飲酒為獻主者執燭抱燋客作而辭然後以授人</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l171' data-llen='5465:5505'>　　<span class='krp-note'>為宵言也主人親執燭敬賓示不倦也/言獻主者客君使宰夫也未爇曰燋</span>執燭不讓</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l172' data-llen='5505:5526'>　　不辭不歌<span class='krp-note'>以燭繼晝禮/殺  少儀</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l173' data-llen='5526:5549'>凡侍坐於君子君子欠伸問日之早晏以食具告改居</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l174' data-llen='5549:5591'>則請退可也<span class='krp-note'>君子謂卿大夫及國中賢者也志倦則欠/體倦則伸問日晏近於久也具猶辯也改</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l175' data-llen='5591:5630'><span class='krp-note'>居謂自變動也古/文伸作信早作蚤</span>夜侍坐問夜膳葷請退可也<span class='krp-note'>問夜問/其時數</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l176' data-llen='5630:5658'><span class='krp-note'>也膳葷謂食之葷辛物蔥薤之/屬食之以止卧古文葷作薰</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l177' data-llen='5658:5684'>　　右請退<span class='krp-note'>本文此下有君賜之/食一條今入臣禮篇</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l178' data-llen='5684:5711'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0086', 'WYG', '015-10b' );" name="015-10b" class="pb">[015-10b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l179' data-llen='5711:5734'>若先生異爵者請見之則辭辭不得命則曰某無以見</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l180' data-llen='5734:5771'>辭不得命將走見先見之<span class='krp-note'>先生致仕者也異爵謂卿大/夫也辭辭其自降而來走猶</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l181' data-llen='5771:5797'><span class='krp-note'>出也先見之者出先拜也曲/禮曰主人敬賓則先拜賓</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l182' data-llen='5797:5837'>　　右長者請見<span class='krp-note'>本文此下有非以君命使一條今入/通禮名器上篇凡執幣執玉一條今</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l183' data-llen='5837:5872'>　　<span class='krp-note'>入曲/禮篇</span>　記士於大夫不敢拜迎而拜送<span class='krp-note'>禮不敵始/來拜則士</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l184' data-llen='5872:5883'>　　<span class='krp-note'>辟也/玉藻</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l185' data-llen='5883:5896'>士相見義　　　　賓禮二</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l186' data-llen='5896:5901'>　補記</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l187' data-llen='5901:5928'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0086', 'WYG', '015-11a' );" name="015-11a" class="pb">[015-11a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l188' data-llen='5928:5951'>自天子至于庶人皆有摯摯者致也所以致其志也天</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l189' data-llen='5951:5974'>子之摯鬯諸侯玉卿羔大夫鴈士雉鬯也者言德之逺</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l190' data-llen='5974:5997'>聞也玉也者言一度不易也羔也者言柔而有禮也鴈</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l191' data-llen='5997:6020'>也者言進退知時也雉也者言死其節也故天子以遠</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l192' data-llen='6020:6043'>德為志諸侯以一度為志卿以有禮為志大夫以進退</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l193' data-llen='6043:6066'>為志士以死節為志明乎志之義而天下治矣故執斯</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l194' data-llen='6066:6089'>摯者致志者也君之摯以事神臣之摯以養人唯君受</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l195' data-llen='6089:6112'>摯者唯君受養也非其君則辭摯不敢當養也古者非</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l196' data-llen='6112:6139'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0086', 'WYG', '015-11b' );" name="015-11b" class="pb">[015-11b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l197' data-llen='6139:6162'>其君不仕非其師不學非其人不友非其大夫不見士</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l198' data-llen='6162:6185'>相見之禮必依於介紹以言其不苟合者也必依於摯</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l199' data-llen='6185:6208'>以言其道可親也苟而合唯小人無恥者能之君子可</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l200' data-llen='6208:6231'>見也不可屈也可親也不可狎也可遠也不可疎也賓</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l201' data-llen='6231:6254'>至門主人三辭見賓稱摯主人三辭摯所以致尊嚴也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l202' data-llen='6254:6277'>大夫以禮相接士以禮相諭庶人以禮相同然而爭奪</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l203' data-llen='6277:6300'>興於末者未之有也人苟悦而相若者末必爭苟簡而</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l204' data-llen='6300:6323'>相親者末必怨是故士相見禮者人道之大也所以使</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l205' data-llen='6323:6350'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0086', 'WYG', '015-12a' );" name="015-12a" class="pb">[015-12a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l206' data-llen='6350:6373'>人重其身而毋邇於辱也所以使人慎其交而毋邇於</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l207' data-llen='6373:6396'>祸也唯仕於君者召而往未仕而見於君者冠而奠摯</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l208' data-llen='6396:6419'>在邦曰市井之臣在野曰草莽之臣君雖召不往也是</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l209' data-llen='6419:6442'>故雖有南面之貴千乘之富士之所以結者禮義而已</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l210' data-llen='6442:6465'>矣利不足稱焉刑罰行於國所誅者好利之人未有好</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l211' data-llen='6465:6488'>利而其俗不亂者也無介而相見君子以為諂故諸侯</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l212' data-llen='6488:6522'>大國九介次國七介小國五介<span class='krp-note'>劉敞補禮白虎通/義見邇  名器下</span>　子</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l213' data-llen='6522:6549'>曰無辭不相接也無禮不相見也欲民之毋相䙝也<span class='krp-note'>辭/所</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l214' data-llen='6549:6576'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0086', 'WYG', '015-12b' );" name="015-12b" class="pb">[015-12b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l215' data-llen='6576:6620'><span class='krp-note'>以通情也禮謂摯也春秋傳曰古者諸侯有/朝聘之事號辭必稱先君以相接也  表記</span>　子云禮</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l216' data-llen='6620:6653'>之先幣帛也欲民之先事而後禄也<span class='krp-note'>此禮謂所執之贄/以見者也既相見</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l217' data-llen='6653:6695'><span class='krp-note'>乃奉幣帛以修好也或/云禮之先辭而後幣帛</span>先財而後禮則民利<span class='krp-note'>財幣帛也/利猶貪也</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l218' data-llen='6695:6725'>無辭而行情則民爭<span class='krp-note'>辭辭讓也情/主利欲也</span>故君子於有饋者弗</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l219' data-llen='6725:6759'>能見則不視其饋<span class='krp-note'>饋遺也不能見謂有/疾也不視猶不内也</span>以此坊民民猶</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l220' data-llen='6759:6786'>貴禄而賤行<span class='krp-note'>行猶事也言務得其/禄不務其事  坊記</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l221' data-llen='6786:6789'>　</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l222' data-llen='6789:6799'>　禮書綱目卷十三</span><br/>
